<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Happy Birthday 💖</title>

<style>
body {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, #ff9a9e, #fad0c4);
    text-align: center;
    color: white;
}

.container {
    padding: 40px;
}

img {
    width: 220px;
    height: 220px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 5px solid white;
    object-fit: cover;
    margin-top: 20px;
}

h1 {
    font-size: 35px;
}

p {
    font-size: 18px;
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: auto;
}

button {
    margin-top: 20px;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    border: none;
    background: white;
    color: #ff4b5c;
    font-size: 16px;
    border-radius: 20px;
}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="container">
    <h1>Happy Birthday Afiya🎉</h1>

    <img src="IMG-20260406-WA0037.jpg" alt="Her Photo">

    <p>
        You are one of the most special people in my life 💖  
        Thank you for always being there for me.  
        I hope your day is filled with happiness and love ✨  
    </p>

    <button onclick="showMessage()">Click Me 💌</button>
</div>

<script>
function showMessage() {
    alert("I’m really lucky to have you 💖 Happy Birthday!");
}
</script>

</body>
</html>
